<div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn" rendition="class:kannada maturity:undetermined">

<!--<h4>First Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/><unclear>sva</unclear>sti śrī yādavanārāyaṇaṁ bhujabaḷapravuḍhapratāpacakravartti
<lb n="2"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> vīrarāmadēvana vijayarājyōdayada yippatta 22 neya
<lb n="3"/><unclear>kha</unclear>rasaṁvatsarada jēṣṭa su 5 guruvāradalu rāya haḍa panā<note n="349-1">The letter ḍa is written above the line in smaller character.</note><note n="349-3">Read vū.</note>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>li bida taṟala masaṇeyanāykaṁge beḷugaliya prabhu dēka
<lb n="6" break="no"/>gauḍa kūṭṭa netarugeyi goṭṭagaḍiya dāriya teṁkage
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ya keṁgāḍa keyi kaṁba 10 pālisuvaru <g type="ddanda">.</g> Ādake yaḷi
<lb n="8" break="no"/>hidavaru gārddhapana prajāpatiya medu sureya sēvisi
<lb n="9" break="no"/>daru maṁgaḷa mahāśrī śrī
</p>

